Build bookworm-lxde sdcard for Radxa rockpi4b:

Input files: ../uboot/out/idbloader.img
             ../uboot/out/uboot.img
             ../uboot/out/trust.img
             ../linux/out/boot.img
             ../rootfs-bookworm/linaro-rootfs.img

./mksdcardimg.sh

The result is in sdcard.img

sudo dd if=./sdcard.img of=/dev/sda bs=4096 conv=notrunc,fsync

